data.title: Supportive of all small businesses in the Santa Clara community
data.text: The entire team at SC Chamber do an outstanding job to help small and large businesses in networking opportunities.  In addition they are continually working to better the community by being pro-active for small businesses.

data.title: Nice Staff
data.text: They do a great job of keeping visitors informed of what there is to do in Santa Clara, as well as helping with conferences.  Staff is very good and with the the San Francisco 49er new stadium in Santa Clara, they expect to be even busier. Stopped by their office very close to the city hall area in the city.

data.title: Saved money
data.text: Picked up tickets to the Winchester Mystery House (just a couple miles away) and saved quite a bit of money.
